title: Hour 2 - More MNF Reaction, Bob Condotta
itunes:title: Hour 2 - More MNF Reaction, Bob Condotta
description:
Dan continues to react to the Denver Broncos' loss to Seattle last night and talks to Seahawks insider Bob Condotta about the reaction the fans had when their former QB, Russell Wilson took to to their field wearing a different uniform.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
